title: How long will take this repair?

embed.description: CtrlV.cz nabízí nejrychlejší ScreenShot a PrintScreen online jen pomocí webového prohlížeče a to bez doplňků.

body: I have plenty of waiting i can't log in to my acc

replies.body:
They're still working on getting that weird Ornn issue fixed up, but from what I hear it's only affecting Mac players currently. 

If you're having problems logging into your account, that probably doesn't have much to do with the Ornn bug. Hit me back up with what's going wrong and I can help troubleshoot a little more!
